OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist and fog quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave another dry day with
OL,7,Fplenty of sunshine. Some fair weather
OL,8,Fcloud will bubble at times, especially
OL,9,Fduring the middle of the day. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarm in the sunshine and light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine end to the day with
OL,13,Fplenty of late sunshine. Overnight
OL,14,Fremaining dry and largely clear
OL,15,Falthough some patchy mist developing
OL,16,Fin places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
