OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry on
OL,6,FWednesday with plenty of sunshine.
OL,7,FFeeling very warm, although a little
OL,8,Fcooler near coasts as sea breezes
OL,9,Fdevelop.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FStaying fine, dry and very warm on
OL,13,FThursday and Friday. Likely to remain
OL,14,Fdry on Saturday although rain may
OL,15,Freach the area later in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
